metadata.name: Love luv Love!
metadata.description:
This work is a fan art of the character "Luv-chan" by the creator Luv.

ラヴちゃんは魅力的な笑顔とスタイルに誰もが惚れてしまう素敵なキャラクターです！

She's a wonderful character whose charming smile and style will make anyone fall in love with her!
